A huge swirling
 --WhirlPool--
 engulfs you
 and your ship
 dragging both
     to a
 watery grave!

As the water
 enters  your
lungs you pass
into Darkness!

You awaken on
 the shores of
 a forgotten
Land.  Your ship
 and crew lost
  to the sea!

 The one way is
   Love, Sol,
 Moons & Death,

A red hot rod

will touch?

Here, friend,
have a drink!
It costs 7 g.p.
You pay?

What? Can't pay!
Out you scum!

Dawn,
the city of
myths & magic!

The conjunction
of the moons
finds link!

Nasty creatures,
  nasty dark,
sure thee ready,
fore thee embark

None return or
 so I'm told,
from the pool,
dark and cold!

Shrines of
  knowledge,
  shrines of
   strength,
 all are lost
into the brink!

Fountains fair
       &
 fountains foul
all are found in
 dungeons bowel

EXODUS:
   Ultima ]I[
 which is next?
Now could it be.

Seek ye out the
 Lord of Time,
and the one way
is a sure find!

<U+0098><<U+0098><U+008E><U+0098>Ù<U+0098><U+0099>    Ye local
     Grocer

Rations:
1 g.p. each.
How many would
you like?

A curing will
cost 100 g.p.
Wilt thou pay?

Healings cost
200 g.p.  Wilt
thou pay?

Resurrections
cost 500 g.p.
Wilt thou pay?

Recallings
cost 900 g.p.
Wilt thou pay?

Without proper
offerings I
cannot help!

I'm sorry, but
thou hast not
gold enough.

<U+009C><U+009C>¯x¯x
Welcome to the
Weapons Shop!

List?

I'm very sorry,
but you haven't
the gold!

Here you are.
May it serve
you well.

You don't own
one of those!

Available:
B:Dagger    5gp
C:Mace     30gp
D:Sling    60gp
E:Axe     125gp
F:Bow     350gp
G:Sword   200gp

I:+2 Axe  400gp
J:+2 Bow 1050gp
K:+2 Swd  800gp
L:Gloves 1200gp
M:+4 Axe 2700gp
N:+4 Bow 6550gp

'PePE
Welcome to the
Armour Shop!

List?

And so the sage
said unto thee
`If thou can
solve my rhyme

you'll learn of
marks & playing
cards & hidden
holy shrines.

Of marks I say
there are but 4
of fire, force,
snake & king.

Learn their use
in Devil Guard,
or death you'll
surely bring.

Shrines there
are again but 4
to which you
go and pray.

Their uses are
inumerable and
clues throughout
I say.

The cards their
suits do number
4, called Sol
Moon, Death
and Love.

Unto the Montors
thou must go
for guidence
from above.

To aid thee in
thy cryptic
search, to
dungeons thou
must fare.

There seek out
the Lord of Time
to help you
if he cares.'

Fare thee well
and good luck!

Ah, too bad.
These are the
best in town!

May you ride
fast and true
friend!

Congratulations!
   Thou hast
   compleated
Exodus: Ultima 3
       in
